{"tid":1385424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"孟子：「自反而縮，雖千萬人吾往矣」","createTime":"2019-07-30T05:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T10:01:56.000Z","uid":58335,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"000838df5c956d28f42da81c14badadb5d3e7e45","tid":1385424,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:30:30.000Z","msg":"今日mtr運動<br />\n聽到有人講民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以咩撚民唔民意就唔使太重視<br />\n要歸邊一早歸曬<br />\n剩底啲乜撚中立其實咪即係藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭先先聽到對偽中立真藍屍夫婦講咩搞去第二到搞，唔好阻到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「自反而縮，雖千萬人吾往矣」出自《孟子‧公孫丑上》。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「自反」解作自我反省，「縮」有理直之意，經過多次反思而於心無愧，縱使面對千軍萬馬，也勇往直前，毫不畏懼。</span></span>此句用來形容龍和道義士們的心境，可謂再適合不過。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://polymerhk.com/articles/2017/10/06/39908/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpolymerhk.com%2Farticles%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F39908%2F&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI6hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=880fd7ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://polymerhk.com/articles/2017/10/06/39908/</a>"},{"pid":"e219e83fd345efa2570a971ab1ceab49eac3dcf4","tid":1385424,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82e83ed8ca0520a2a7c2eb1b1963369d562073c","tid":1385424,"uid":109794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:37:27.000Z","msg":"PUSH!!!<br />\nBTW<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請入 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dsPmtT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dsPmtT</a> 幫手推post!!<br />\n一齊report 9 藍絲 fb pages, 斷佢地輿論!!!!!<br />\n一人一Report, 搞到佢地摺埋!!!